## State Ownership (post-2026-05-04 PM-orchestrator architecture)

- **PM** owns `_state.md` writes via `Bash("ai-kit sdlc state update --op ...")` — 6 ops via discriminator (field/progress/kpi/log/status/stage_rollback)
- **Skills** create initial `_state.md` via `ai-kit sdlc scaffold {workspace|module|feature|hotfix}` (new-feature, from-doc, hotfix); seal via `ai-kit sdlc state update --op status --status done` (close-feature)
- **Agents** return verdict JSON to PM — they do NOT write `_state.md` directly
- **dispatcher.md** is reference playbook (deprecated as callable agent per AGENTS.md:27); PM reads sections on-demand for routing/validation logic

